description: Number of divisors of n! which are also differences between consecutive divisors of n! (ordered by size).
references: D. Berend et al. (1993): Gaps between consecutive divisors of factorials, Ann. Inst. Fourier, 43(3):569-583.
author: _Labos Elemer_, Apr 23 2001
extensions: One more term from _Robert G. Wilson v_, Jan 29 2002
